      "updated": 1782245037324,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Support uploads / downloads, async/streaming responses <-- drops sandbox command entirely, just becomes a regular worker\n\nAdd: iii trigger --timeout 60. Max time to wait (60s default) for an initial response on an async call before aborting.\n",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": "jWR8ojh8X-cReWzjWr_Qv",
      "originalText": "Support uploads / downloads, async/streaming responses <-- drops sandbox command entirely, just becomes a regular worker\n\nAdd: iii trigger --timeout 60. Max time to wait (60s default) for an initial response on an async call before aborting.\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
