      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Starts each worker with the\nconfiguration as defined in worker-\ncompose.yaml\n\nUses iii worker start to do so.\n\nIs a long-running process, while it\nis running the workers stay up.\nWhen it exits the workers\nshutdown.",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "jlmIviOS7PHokx7bwh8a1",
      "originalText": "Starts each worker with the configuration as defined in worker-compose.yaml\n\nUses iii worker start to do so.\n\nIs a long-running process, while it is running the workers stay up. When it exits the workers shutdown.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
