      "text": "Daemonize iii worker compose.\nResponds to normal SIG\ncommands.\n\nWrites PID to standard for system\n(ex. /run/user/UID/worker-\ncompose.pid), prints PID, and\nexits.",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "D6vnzuH0zkQ66_yGfl5D8",
      "originalText": "Daemonize iii worker compose. Responds to normal SIG commands.\n\nWrites PID to standard for system (ex. /run/user/UID/worker-compose.pid), prints PID, and exits.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
