      "text": "iii worker compose is essentially the\nsame functionality as iii has for\nstarting workers\n\nBut a separate long-running\nprocess with docker-like control",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "JNawk4p2deJh3vUpow38y",
      "originalText": "iii worker compose is essentially the same functionality as iii has for starting workers\n\nBut a separate long-running process with docker-like control",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
